name: Fearless Tyune
description:
Inspired by the Muisca story of the goddess Bachue and her disagreement with the goddess Chia, the story relates that Bachue decides to return to Iguaque Lake, to enter the lake she must go through a temple, infested with possessed chia fanatics, Bachue asks his faithful companion that clears the temple of these beings.

This game is still in development.  Early access version uploaded for submission to the Mytholojam 2019 and Low spec Jam.
